item.title: CVE-2017-8569|2024-08-05T16:41:23.477Z -- microsoft%20corporation -- microsoft%20sharepoint%20enterprise%20server%202016
item.description: Microsoft SharePoint Server allows an elevation of privilege vulnerability due to the way that it sanitizes a specially crafted web request to an affected SharePoint server, aka "SharePoint Server XSS Vulnerability".
